The paper discusses the application of network embedding methods for machine learning on road networks, which involves analyzing the structure of the network. This suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Databases (cs.DB), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI).
